<li>Wilds<br>
[:en] # About Hook’s Heroes<br>
In this wild slot machine we follow one-eyed pirates on an adventure on the seven seas. With Caribbean themed background music, you quickly get into the right mood and the lavish special effects very much enhances the game experience. Hook’s Heroes is mostly famous for its well made Free Spins game and with three different features to choose from you never get bored while playing. Ship ahoy!</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="game-features">Game Features</h2>
<p>The slot machine consists of five reels with three rows and treats the player with wilds, Free Spins with three different colourful features and the Single Feature Spin.</p>
<h3 id="wild-2">Wild</h3>
<p>The wild symbol replaces all other symbols except the Free Spins symbol and can appear in both the main game as well as during Free Spins.</p>
<h3 id="free-spins">Free Spins</h3>
<p>The Free Spins game is really something else. Here you get the choice between three different varieties. When you manage to hit at least three Free Spins symbols in the main game you are awarded with the Free Spins. If you hit four or five Free Spins symbols you are awarded with choosing the Free Spins feature two and three times respectively.</p>
<h4 id="fairy-feature-–-7-free-spins.">Fairy Feature – 7 Free Spins.</h4>
<p>During each and every spin a number of 2-5 random symbols are transformed into wilds. The feeling of getting five wilds in a row is pretty much the best thing ever.</p>
<h4 id="mermaid-feature---10-free-spins.">Mermaid Feature - 10 Free Spins.</h4>
<p>All winnings are doubled and if you get a winning bet line that includes one wild or more you’ll collect four times the win!</p>
<h4 id="pirate-feature---15-free-spins.">Pirate Feature - 15 Free Spins.</h4>
<p>This feature counts all of the same types of symbols, regardless of their position in the game. It means that the symbols aren’t required to follow a winning bet line to award you with the win.</p>
<h3 id="single-feature-spin-2">Single Feature Spin</h3>
<p>If you hit two freespins symbols in the main game one of the freespins features is activated for one spin.</p>
